        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Xill matriarchs are paragons of their kind, having undergone a ritualistic metamorphosis involving the consumption of brain matter from xill egg hosts. The matriarchs possess powerful mental abilities, which they use to protect the young of their race."
        }
    ],
